Installation
------------

This plugin can be installed via:

    python -m pip install {{ cookiecutter.distribution_name }}

As long as you have not explicitly added a `PLUGINS` setting to your Pelican settings file, then the newly-installed plugin should be automatically detected and enabled. Otherwise, you must add `{{ cookiecutter.package_name }}` to your existing `PLUGINS` list. For more information, please see the [How to Use Plugins](https://docs.getpelican.com/en/latest/plugins.html#how-to-use-plugins) documentation.

